A massive metallic shield shaped like a hexagonal database icon hovers protectively over a sleek server rack, while swarms of tiny red geometric virus shapes bounce harmlessly off its gleaming surface, some disintegrating into particles on impact. The scene is rendered in deep cyberpunk style with neon purple and electric blue lighting cutting through atmospheric haze, chrome reflections, and holographic scan lines sweeping across the shield. The server beneath glows with warm amber light through its ventilation grilles, humming with power and speed. Dark industrial background with exposed pipes and cables, rain-slicked surfaces reflecting the neon glow.
